Select CONCAT(    bp.code, ' ', (Select trans.message_value from meta_translation trans where trans.message_key = CONCAT('value:', bp.name) AND trans.language = COALESCE(:logisticalForm.deliverToCustomerPartner.language.code,'en'))) From stock_stock_move_line self Left join base_product bp on self.product = bp.id Where self.finished_product IN      (          Select sm.id          FROM stock_stock_move_line as sm          WHERE sm.product = :stockMoveLine.product.id            AND sm.tracking_number = :stockMoveLine.trackingNumber.id            AND sm.produced_manuf_order IS NOT NULL      )  AND self.consumed_manuf_order IS NOT NULL

Select COALESCE(stn.tracking_number_seq, '') From stock_stock_move_line self Left join stock_tracking_number stn on self.tracking_number = stn.id Where self.finished_product IN      (          Select sm.id          FROM stock_stock_move_line as sm          WHERE sm.product = :stockMoveLine.product.id            AND sm.tracking_number = :stockMoveLine.trackingNumber.id            AND sm.produced_manuf_order IS NOT NULL      ) AND self.consumed_manuf_order IS NOT NULL

Select    CONCAT(        (Select metaSelectItem.title               From meta_select_item metaSelectItem                Join meta_select metaSelect on metaSelectItem.select_id = metaSelect.id               Where metaSelect.name = 'logistical.form.line.type.select'                 AND metaSelectItem.value = CAST(:typeSelect AS varchar(255))),        ' No.',        self.parcel_pallet_number        ) From stock_logistical_form_line self Where self.id = :id;

Select       CASE           WHEN ssml.tracking_number IS NOT NULL THEN               CONCAT(                       (Select trans.message_value                        From meta_translation trans                        Where trans.message_key = concat('value:', :stockMoveLine.product.name)                          AND trans.language = COALESCE(:logisticalForm.deliverToCustomerPartner.language.code, 'en')                        limit 1),                       E'\n',                       stn.tracking_number_seq                   )           ELSE               (Select trans.message_value                From meta_translation trans                Where trans.message_key = concat('value:', :stockMoveLine.product.name)                  AND trans.language = COALESCE(:logisticalForm.deliverToCustomerPartner.language.code, 'en')                limit 1)           END From stock_logistical_form_line self         LEFT Join stock_stock_move_line ssml on self.stock_move_line = ssml.id        LEFT JOIN stock_tracking_number stn on ssml.tracking_number = stn.id Where self.id = :id;
Select count(self) From LogisticalFormLine self Where self.logisticalForm.id = :id AND self.typeSelect = 2
Select sum(self.grossMass) from LogisticalFormLine self Where self.logisticalForm.id = :id AND self.typeSelect = 2

Select       CASE           WHEN ssml.tracking_number IS NOT NULL THEN               CONCAT(                       (Select trans.message_value                        From meta_translation trans                        Where trans.message_key = concat('value:', :stockMoveLine.product.name)                          AND trans.language = COALESCE(:logisticalForm.deliverToCustomerPartner.language.code, 'en')                        limit 1),                       E'\n',                       stn.tracking_number_seq                   )           ELSE               (Select trans.message_value                From meta_translation trans                Where trans.message_key = concat('value:', :stockMoveLine.product.name)                  AND trans.language = COALESCE(:logisticalForm.deliverToCustomerPartner.language.code, 'en')                limit 1)           END From stock_logistical_form_line self         LEFT Join stock_stock_move_line ssml on self.stock_move_line = ssml.id        LEFT JOIN stock_tracking_number stn on ssml.tracking_number = stn.id Where self.id = :id;

Select    CONCAT(        (Select metaSelectItem.title               From meta_select_item metaSelectItem                Join meta_select metaSelect on metaSelectItem.select_id = metaSelect.id               Where metaSelect.name = 'logistical.form.line.type.select'                 AND metaSelectItem.value = CAST(:typeSelect AS varchar(255))),        ' No.',        self.parcel_pallet_number        ) From stock_logistical_form_line self Where self.id = :id;

Select COALESCE(stn.tracking_number_seq, '') From stock_stock_move_line self Left join stock_tracking_number stn on self.tracking_number = stn.id Where self.finished_product IN      (          Select sm.id          FROM stock_stock_move_line as sm          WHERE sm.product = :stockMoveLine.product.id            AND sm.tracking_number = :stockMoveLine.trackingNumber.id            AND sm.produced_manuf_order IS NOT NULL      ) AND self.consumed_manuf_order IS NOT NULL

Select CONCAT(    bp.code, ' ', (Select trans.message_value from meta_translation trans where trans.message_key = CONCAT('value:', bp.name) AND trans.language = COALESCE(:logisticalForm.deliverToCustomerPartner.language.code,'en'))) From stock_stock_move_line self Left join base_product bp on self.product = bp.id Where self.finished_product IN      (          Select sm.id          FROM stock_stock_move_line as sm          WHERE sm.product = :stockMoveLine.product.id            AND sm.tracking_number = :stockMoveLine.trackingNumber.id            AND sm.produced_manuf_order IS NOT NULL      )  AND self.consumed_manuf_order IS NOT NULL
Select CASE WHEN self.typeSelect = 3 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END From LogisticalFormLine self Where self.id = :id
Select sum(self.grossMass) from LogisticalFormLine self Where self.logisticalForm.id = :id AND self.typeSelect = 2
